HONEI DROID

=== Things you need ===
Recent versions of a Java SDK, Apache Ant, Google Android SDK and Google Android NDK.

=== Build system setup ===
Copy local.properties.sample to local.properties.
Replace $PATH_TO_YOUR_ANDROID_SDK by the path to your Android SDK.
Make sure that your $PATH includes "tools" and "platform-tools" of the Android SDK and the root of the Android NDK.

=== Building ===
"ant debug" starts a debug build.
"ant release" starts a release build.
"ant install" starts a debug build and uploads the binary to a running android emulator instance.
Make sure to start an emulator instance via "android" before running "ant install".

Further details can be found on the official android sdk help; this project resembles the Android project layout 
